		     to public.plain-text so mail/Files/Safari offer ChessEver as an
		     editor. The OS forwards the file URL via the SceneDelegate to the
		     app_links plugin; DeepLinkService routes file:// URIs into
		     PgnFileIntakeService. Set to false so iOS copies the file into
